description:
Season 2... we have arrived!


Things may look slightly different, can you tell?


but wer'e back and ready to bring you all the tea for the last week or so.

Did you know who Dream was until this moment? Did you watch Hailey Bieber and Alice Coopers interview? Are you anti-maroon 5 now? Is Kanye just crazy or proving a point?


here's our thoughts and all things that matter pop culture this week, now give us yours!!
